summary: FDO end-to-end testing with PostgreSQL backend
description: |
    Comprehensive FDO testing with PostgreSQL database covering:
    - Certificate infrastructure setup
    - Multi-server orchestration (manufacturer, rendezvous, owner)
    - PostgreSQL database integration
    - Device initialization and onboarding
    - ServiceInfo module testing
    - Protocol validation with database persistence

test: ../../rpm/test-onboarding-postgres.sh

framework: shell

duration: 30m

tag:
  - fdo
  - e2e
  - protocol
  - onboarding
  - postgres
  - database
  - rpm
